    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(…) Et dua <emph>berva sigillata</emph> temporibus domni <persName
                            ref="#people/338" key="#Princeps">Guaimari</persName> gratia <rs
                            key="#Princeps">principis</rs>: contineba ipsa scripta sigillata, ut
                            <name ref="Angelbertus filius Leoni">Angelpertus</name> filius Leoni de
                        locu Baniara, ut omne <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Public_exactions #Datium #Servitium #Tolls"
                            >datione, et petitione, et portaticum, et excaticum, plateaticum, seum
                            et omne servitium</rs> quod nostri Palatiu facere undecumque debueritis,
                        ut infra totum <rs key="#Actio">actum</rs> nostro <placeName
                            ref="#places/84"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Actio #Public_exactions #Datium #Servitium"
                            >Salernitano</placeName> emeritis aut benumdederitis, integrum ipsum
                        plateaticum tuo et de tuis heredibus etbeniad potestate, et aliut contineba
                        ipsa scripta sigillata.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
